      "description": "We are pleased to present this exceptional vehicle, maintained to the highest standards. Its condition is impeccable, reflecting a level of care that borders on the extraordinary. Every detail, from the pristine exterior finish to the untouched interior, confirms its status as a premier example of its class. This is an investment-grade opportunity for the discerning driver who demands nothing less than excellence.",
      "price": 44800.0,
